ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of VIRGINIA GREENE of Vancouver, British Columbia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission, representing the region set out in subparagraph 11(3)(a)(vi) of the Act, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years on a part-time basis, in the place of Andrew Wilkinson.
